      <preamble>
         <formula name="enactingText">
            <p>The Scottish Ministers make the following Regulations in exercise of the powers conferred by sections 11 and 16(2) of the Local Governance (Scotland) Act 2004<noteRef href="#f00001" class="footnote" marker="1"/> and all other powers enabling them to do so.</p>
         </formula>
      </preamble>
      <body>
         <hcontainer name="regulation" eId="regulation-1">
            <heading>Citation and commencement</heading>
            <num>1.</num>
            <content>
               <p>These Regulations may be cited as the Local Governance (Scotland) Act 2004 (Remuneration) Amendment Regulations 2019 and come into force on 1 April 2019.</p>
            </content>
         </hcontainer>
         <hcontainer name="regulation" eId="regulation-2">
            <heading>Amendment of the Local Governance (Scotland) Act 2004 (Remuneration) Regulations 2007</heading>
            <num>2.</num>
            <paragraph eId="regulation-2-1">
               <num>(1)</num>
               <content>
                  <p>The Local Governance (Scotland) Act 2004 (Remuneration) Regulations 2007<noteRef href="#f00002" class="footnote" marker="2"/> are amended as follows.</p>
               </content>
            </paragraph>
            <paragraph eId="regulation-2-2">
               <num>(2)</num>
               <content>
                  <p>For the table in regulation 6(2) (remuneration of the Leader of the Council) substitute—<mod>
                        <quotedStructure startQuote="“" endQuote="”" ukl:TargetClass="secondary" ukl:TargetSubClass="regulation" ukl:Context="main">
                           <tblock class="tabular" ukl:Orientation="portrait">
                              <foreign>
                                 <table xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" cols="2">
                                    <colgroup>
                                       <col width="29.7pt"/>
                                       <col width="364.35pt"/>
                                    </colgroup>
                                    <tbody>
                                       <tr>
                                          <td rowspan="1" colspan="1">(a)</td>
                                          <td rowspan="1" colspan="1">Band A – £29,119,</td>
                                       </tr>
                                       <tr>
                                          <td rowspan="1" colspan="1">(b)</td>
                                          <td rowspan="1" colspan="1">Band B – £34,944,</td>
                                       </tr>
                                       <tr>
                                          <td rowspan="1" colspan="1">(c)</td>
                                          <td rowspan="1" colspan="1">Band C – £40,765,</td>
                                       </tr>
                                       <tr>
                                          <td rowspan="1" colspan="1">(d)</td>
                                          <td rowspan="1" colspan="1">Band D – £52,414.</td>
                                       </tr>
                                    </tbody>
                                 </table>
                              </foreign>
                           </tblock>
                        </quotedStructure>
                     </mod>
                     <inline name="AppendText">.</inline>
                  </p>
               </content>
            </paragraph>
            <paragraph eId="regulation-2-3">
               <num>(3)</num>
               <content>
                  <p>For the table in regulation 7(2) (remuneration of the Civic Head) substitute—<mod>
                        <quotedStructure startQuote="“" endQuote="”" ukl:TargetClass="secondary" ukl:TargetSubClass="regulation" ukl:Context="main">
                           <tblock class="tabular" ukl:Orientation="portrait">
                              <foreign>
                                 <table xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" cols="2">
                                    <colgroup>
                                       <col width="28.35pt"/>
                                       <col width="364.35pt"/>
                                    </colgroup>
                                    <tbody>
                                       <tr>
                                          <td rowspan="1" colspan="1">(a)</td>
                                          <td rowspan="1" colspan="1">Band A – £21,840,</td>
                                       </tr>
                                       <tr>
                                          <td rowspan="1" colspan="1">(b)</td>
                                          <td rowspan="1" colspan="1">Band B – £26,208,</td>
                                       </tr>
                                       <tr>
                                          <td rowspan="1" colspan="1">(c)</td>
                                          <td rowspan="1" colspan="1">Band C – £30,575,</td>
                                       </tr>
                                       <tr>
                                          <td rowspan="1" colspan="1">(d)</td>
                                          <td rowspan="1" colspan="1">Band D – £39,310.</td>
                                       </tr>
                                    </tbody>
                                 </table>
                              </foreign>
                           </tblock>
                        </quotedStructure>
                     </mod>
                     <inline name="AppendText">.</inline>
                  </p>
               </content>
            </paragraph>
            <paragraph eId="regulation-2-4">
               <num>(4)</num>
               <content>
                  <p>In regulation 10 (councillors’ remuneration) for “£16,994” substitute “£17,470”.</p>
               </content>
            </paragraph>
            <paragraph eId="regulation-2-5">
               <num>(5)</num>
               <intro>
                  <p>In regulation 12 (joint boards)—</p>
               </intro>
               <subparagraph eId="regulation-2-5-a">
                  <num>(a)</num>
                  <content>
                     <p>in paragraph (8) (payment to conveners) for “£21,245” substitute “£21,840”, and</p>
                  </content>
               </subparagraph>
               <subparagraph eId="regulation-2-5-b">
                  <num>(b)</num>
                  <content>
                     <p>in paragraph (9) (payment to vice-conveners) for “£20,183” substitute “£20,748”.</p>
                  </content>
               </subparagraph>
            </paragraph>
